  "name": "Stone Tell",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>This spell allows the caster to speak with stones in the same manner as plants are conversed with via <em>speak to plants</em>. The stones relate to the character who or what has touched them as well as revealing what is covered or concealed behind or under them. The stones relate complete descriptions if asked. Note that a stone's perspective, perception, and knowledge may prevent the stone from providing the details the character is looking for. The character can speak with natural or worked stone.</p>",
